
FOLLOW YOUR FEAR

forget fear is fear
remember that fear is exciting
remember fear is rush
and fear can be change
remember intelligent fear

some fear can be true
some fear can be warning fear
some fear can be dangerous
stay away from the dangerous fear

remember that good fear
can lead to good things

there IS a fine distinction of
good fear
and
bad fear

good fear usually means
opportunities
the new
experiences
change
being alive

so try it
whatever 'it' is, do it
"follow your fear"